Maintainer: Yi Liu <yi.iu.biostat@gmail.com>
Description: The package implements the propensity score weighted estimators for several 
	     causal estimands from the classes of weighted ATE, weighted ATT and weighted ATC. 
             For binary outcomes, we also extend the methods to output the results on weighted 
             risk ratio (RR), weighted risk ratio (RR) and weighted odds ratio (OR). 
